ature in 2024.AP Photo/Andy Manis\r\n<ul><li>Democrats are working to break GOP legislative supermajorities in 2024.</li><li>The party had a b… [+3172 chars]','2023-12-17 14:50:35',1,'2023-12-25 17:08:44','2023-12-25 17:08:44'),(103,'New Hope — and an Old Hurdle — for a Terrible Disease With Terrible Treatments','new-hope-and-an-old-hurdle-for-a-terrible-disease-with-terrible-treatments',90,4,14,'Researchers in developing countries are trying to find treatments for conditions that affect the poorest people. But the system is stacked against their therapies.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/12/19/health/leishmaniasis-fly-treatment-colombia.html','https://via.placeholder.com/150','\n        <div class=\'article-content\'>\n            <h5 class=\'article-content__text\'>\n                Three years ago, Jesús Tilano went to a hospital in a thickly forested valley in Colombia with large open lesions on his nose, right arm and left hand. He was diagnosed with leishmaniasis, a parasitic disease that is spread in the bite of a female sand fly and which plagues poor people who work in fields or forests across developing countries.\n            </h5>\n            <div>\n            <p class=\'snipit-class\'>\n                Researchers in developing countries are trying to find treatments for conditions that affect the poorest people. But the system is stacked against their therapies.\n            </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>','2023-12-19 03:01:01',1,'2023-12-25 17:08:48','2023-12-25 17:08:48'),(104,'Vibe Check','vibe-check',91,1,5,'Business Insider surveyed Gen Z to find out how the most connected generation in history is redefining economic and social norms. Check out the results.','https://www.businessinsider.com/vibe-check-gen-z-survey-data-2023-12','https://i.insider.com/657b3fec50edbc52a8644755?width=1200','!(function () {\n\'use strict\';\nwindow.addEventListener(\'message\', function (e) {\nif (void 0 !== e.data[\'datawrapper-height\']) {\nvar t = docume