class=\'article-content\'>\n            <h5 class=\'article-content__text\'>\n                A federal judge in Texas on Monday upheld a ban that prevented state employees from using TikTok, the Chinese-owned short-form video app, on government devices and networks, rejecting a challenge by lawyers who argued that the prohibition had violated the First Amendment.\n            </h5>\n            <div>\n            <p class=\'snipit-class\'>\n                The Texas law was challenged by First Amendment lawyers who filed a suit on behalf of college professors who said that their work had been compromised when they lost access to the app.\n            </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>','2023-12-11 21:54:03',1,'2023-12-25 17:11:19','2023-12-25 17:11:19'),(159,'Slate Money Goes to the Movies: Jerry Maguire','slate-money-goes-to-the-movies-jerry-maguire',139,1,22,'How real-world sports agents do business.','https://slate.com/podcasts/slate-money/2023/12/does-the-classic-tom-cruise-football-film-hold-up','https://compote.slate.com/images/bb44330d-b6d6-4ba7-b5d3-------99d11f5996ad.jpeg?width=1560&rect=1560x1040&offset=0x0','This week, sports journalist Mina Kimes joins the huddle with Felix Salmon, Emily Peck, and Elizabeth Spiers to discuss the 90s football rom-com Jerry Maguire. Mina explains how real-world sports age… [+487 chars]','2023-12-04 05:00:00',1,'2023-12-25 17:11:21','2023-12-25 17:11:21'),(160,'Google’s Next Top Model, Will the Cybertruck Crash? and This Week in A.I.','googles-next-top-model-will-the-cybertruck-crash-and-this-week-in-ai',140,7,14,'Like the Cybertruck, this podcast is bulletproof.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/12/08/podcasts/hardfork-google-gemini-cybertruck.html','https://via.placeholder.com/150','\n        <div class=\'article-content\'>\n            <h5 class=\'article-content__text\'>\n                Warning: this episode contains strong language.\n            </h5>\n            <div>\n            <p class=\'snipit-class\'>\n   