re going to have to work 10 times harder.” This is how my father prepared me for being black in America.\n            </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>','2019-01-17 17:19:26',1,'2023-12-25 17:11:53','2023-12-25 17:11:53'),(171,'Bandai Namco Entertainment invests in more U.S. game startups','bandai-namco-entertainment-invests-in-more-us-game-startups',149,2,19,'Bandai Namco\'s 021 Fund said it has invested in two additional U.S. game startups -- Flickplay and Code Charm.','https://venturebeat.com/games/bandai-namco-invests-in-more-u-s-game-startups/','https://venturebeat.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/【logo】021-logo-only_new.jpg?w=1200&strip=all','Are you looking to showcase your brand in front of the brightest minds of the gaming industry? Consider getting a custom GamesBeat sponsorship. Learn more.\r\nBandai Namcos 021 Fund said it has investe… [+1283 chars]','2023-11-27 19:00:00',1,'2023-12-25 17:11:53','2023-12-25 17:11:53'),(172,'Other Voices, Other Worlds','other-voices-other-worlds',150,8,14,'The lineup for this year’s PEN World Voices Festival of International Literature was announced today at an event held in the beautiful courtyard of the Instituto Cervantes in New York.','https://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/03/25/other-voices-other-worlds/','https://via.placeholder.com/150','\n        <div class=\'article-content\'>\n            <h5 class=\'article-content__text\'>\n                The lineup for this year’s PEN World Voices Festival of International Literature was announced today at an event held in the beautiful courtyard of the Instituto Cervantes in New York.\n            </h5>\n            <div>\n            <p class=\'snipit-class\'>\n                The lineup for this year’s PEN World Voices Festival of International Literature was announced today at an event held in the beautiful courtyard of the Instituto Cervantes in New York.\n            </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>','2009-03-25 15:33:21',1,'2023-12-25 17:11:58','2023-12-25 17:11:58'),(173,'Kek Entertainment secures $8M to drive cross-platform gaming','kek-entertainment-secures-8m-to-drive-cross-platform-gaming',149,2,19,'Kek Entertainment has raised $8 million in funding to foster cross-platform gaming experiences across mobile devices, consoles and PCs.','https://venturebeat.com/gaming-business/kek-entertainment-secures-8m-to-drive-cross-platform-gaming/','https://venturebeat.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kek-unit-concept2-1.jpg?w=1200&strip=all','Are you looking to showcase your brand in front of the brightest minds of the gaming industry? Consider getting a custom GamesBeat sponsorship. Learn more.\r\nKek Entertainment has raised $8 million in… [+853 chars]','2023-11-28 09:30:00',1,'2023-12-25 17:11:58','2023-12-25 17:11:58'),(174,'Other Countries, Other Shores','other-countries-other-shores',151,8,14,'C. P. Cavafy makes no explicit reference to himself in his best and most stirring work; and yet, with every poem we read, we cannot help thinking of him.','https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/22/books/review/other-countries-other-shores.html','https://via.placeholder.com/150','\n        <div class=\'article-content\'>\n            <h5 class=\'article-content__text\'>\n                We love poets for the things their poems lead us to imagine; but equally, we love them for how we imagine their lives to be. Confusing poets’ lives with their work is an illusion as old as the tradition of confusing words with objects. But in fact it is for the sake of this illusion that we feel such a strong need for poetry, for novels, for literature. There are some poets whose work we read with their lives in mind, and what we know of those lives ensures that their poetry leaves a more enduring impression. C. P. Cavafy is, for me, just such a poet. Like Edgar Allan Poe, like Franz Kafka, Cavafy makes no explicit reference to himself in his best and most stirring work; and yet, with every poem we read, we cannot help thinking of him.\n            </h5>\n            <div>\n            <p class=\'snipit-class\'>\n                C. P. Cavafy makes no explicit reference to himself in his best and most stirring work; and yet, with every poem we read, we cannot help thinking of him.\n            </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>','2013-12-19 18:16:11',1,'2023-12-25 17:12:03','2023-12-25 17:12:03'),(175,'Take $100 Off This Roku Streambar and Wireless Bass Bundle for the Holidays - CNET','take-100-off-this-roku-streambar-and-wireless-bass-bundle-for-the-holidays-cnet',152,2,9,'Now you can revamp your entertainment space with 4K streaming and premium Dolby Audio for just $150.','https://www.cnet.com/deals/take-100-off-this-roku-streambar-and-wireless-bass-bundle-for-the-holidays/','https://www.cnet.com/a/img/resize/174939f23fb3881f908b0ce7ce0016fa5d0d22c8/hub/2023/12/08/f73aa09b-0d7d-4fd0-a0b3-a948433adf2d/artboard-6-1.png?auto=webp&fit=crop&height=675&width=1200','Looking to upgrade your entertainment space? Adding a soundbar can go a long way in improving your audio, but having the right streaming system is also a major factor in user experience. Amazon is co… [+1229 chars]','2023-12-08 10:36:21',1,'2023-12-25 17:12:04','2023-12-25 17:12:04'),(176,'The Other Side of the Other Wizard','the-other-side-of-the-other-wizard',153,8,14,'Until a recent locker-room confrontation with his teammate Gilbert Arenas, Javaris Crittenton was an anonymous backup guard with a short résumé.','https://www.nytimes.com/2010/01/21/sports/basketball/21wizards.html','https://via.placeholder.com/150','\n        <div class=\'article-content\'>\n            <h5 class=\'article-content__text\'>\n                Gilbert Arenas has the fame and the lavish contract, the All-Star credentials and the clever nicknames. His puckish reputation is so well established that even a felony gun charge can be plausibly cast as a misguided practical joke.\n            </h5>\n            <div>\n            <p class=\'snipit-class\'>\n                Until a recent locker-room confrontation with his teammate Gilbert Arenas, Javaris Crittenton was an anonymous backup guard with a short résumé.\n            </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>','2010-01-20 22:16:48',1,'2023-12-25 17:12:08','2023-12-25 17:12:08'),(177,'America is on the brink in the first trailer for Alex Garland’s Civil War','america-is-on-the-brink-in-the-first-trailer-for-alex-garlands-civil-war',154,2,1,'A24 has released the first trailer for Civil War, directed by Alex Garland (Ex Machina, Men, Annihilation) and starring Kirsten Dunst.','https://www.theverge.com/23999689/civil-war-trailer-alex-garland-a24','https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7lcs9XkWRml0N8O_2Nx9jrBMtMk=/0x0:6000x4000/1200x628/filters:focal(2648x2011:2649x2012)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25159640/Civil_War___First_Image.jpg','America is on the brink in the first trailer for Alex Garlands Civil War\r\nAmerica is on the brink in the first trailer for Alex Garlands Civil War\r\n / The film stars Kirsten Dunst and hits theaters i… [+1251 chars]','2023-12-13 09:01:51',1,'2023-12-25 17:12:09','2023-12-25 17:12:09'),(178,'Other Voices, Other Selves','other-voices-other-selves',155,8,14,'The quirky pleasures in these essays are due in part to Zadie Smith’s inspired cultural references, from Simone Weil to “Buffy the Vampire Slayer.”','https://www.nytimes.com/2010/01/17/books/review/Mishra-t.html','https://via.placeholder.com/150','\n        <div class=\'article-content\'>\n            <h5 class=\'article-content__text\'>\n                “To write critically in English,” Zadie Smith asserts in the opening essay of “Changing My Mind,” “is to aspire to neutrality, to the high style of, say, Lionel Trilling or Edmund Wilson.” Praising Zora Neale Hurston, Smith complains that the mandarin critical mode elevates the experiences of white people to the norm while making “black women talking about a black book” look sectarian. Smith’s own way of escaping this narrow assumption is to declare boldly, “Fact is, I am a black woman.” A writer like Hurston, Smith adds, makes “ ‘black woman-ness’ appear a real, tangible quality, an essence I can almost believe I share, however improbably, with millions of complex individuals.” Hurston also allows Smith “to say things I wouldn’t normally — things like “She is my sister and I love her.” \n            </h5>\n            <div>\n            <p class=\'snipit-class\'>\n                The quirky pleasures in these essays are due in part to Zadie Smith’s inspired cultural references, from Simone Weil to “Buffy the Vampire Slayer.”\n            </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>','2010-01-14 15:40:02',1,'2023-12-25 17:12:13','2023-12-25 17:12:13'),(179,'Chick-fil-A appears to be creating an entertainment app to host video series and podcasts','chick-fil-a-appears-to-be-creating-an-entertainment-app-to-host-video-series-and-podcasts',23,2,5,'Job posting reveals Chick-fil-A\'s plan for a new entertainment app featuring scripted and non-scripted programming.','https://www.businessinsider.com/chick-fil-a-to-launch-play-a-family-entertainment-app-2023-11','https://i.insider.com/6568a45247f9ecb37d88a360?width=1200&format=jpeg','Chick-fil-A short filmChick-fil-A screenshot\r\n<ul><li>Chick-fil-A, one of the most successful fast food chains in the US, is entering showbiz. </li><li>The chain is hiring an \"entertainment producer,… [+2898 chars]','2023-11-30 13:53:56',1,'2023-12-25 17:12:14','2023-12-25 17:12:14'),(180,'Other Cases and Other Questions','other-cases-and-other-questions',156,8,14,'Article examines other cases unrelated to crossing accidents in which Union Pacific has been accused of mishandling evidence (M)','https://www.nytimes.com/2004/07/11/us/other-cases-and-other-questions.html','https://via.placeholder.com/150','\n        <div class=\'article-content\'>\n            <h5 class=\'article-content__text\'>\n                Union Pacific has been accused of mishandling evidence not just in crossin